From: Michal Schmidt <>
Subject: Re: [PATCH] ppp_mppe: Don't put InterimKey on the stack
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
